(and didn't come to this world.)

25
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:22,480
It turns out

26
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:24,560
you are the constables
from Daoming Court.

27
00:01:25,480 --> 00:01:27,400
Considering your merits
in solving cases,

28
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:28,800
I will forget about

29
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:30,400
