Hedgehog.

34
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,160
Are you alright?

35
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:35,360
Come on.

36
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,240
Get up first.

37
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,600
You're not mad at me

38
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:45,640
