Isn't this too spicy?

152
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:15,320
Is it?

153
00:09:17,680 --> 00:09:18,440
Cheers.

154
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:19,440
Cheers.

155
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:26,720
Witch.

156
